strings:
<voice_0x01001CC5><se_high>Princess Medea: Is that you, <hero>?
Is it really you?
<voice_0x01001CC6><se_high>Princess Medea: What do you think it means, us meeting like this, <hero>?
<voice_0x01001CC7><se_high>Princess Medea: It was late, and I was thinking about wanting to talk to you, but I must have fallen asleep...

<voice_0x01001CC8><se_high>Princess Medea: Are we dreaming?
We must be!

<voice_0x01001CC9><se_high>Princess Medea: Do you think this is another effect of the
spring water?

<voice_0x01001CCA><se_high>Princess Medea: I really wanted to talk to you about
Prince Charmless<endash> ...I mean, Charmles.
<voice_0x01001C6D><se_high>Princess Medea: But... Do you think people can change after they get married?
<voice_0x01001C6F><se_high>Princess Medea: I know, <hero>, I know. I could also be quite self-centred when I was younger.
<voice_0x01001C71><se_high>Princess Medea: Perhaps Prince Charmles will grow out of it, too...
